            "type": "text",
            "text": " before any side effect occurs. Parsing extracts intent; validation catches schema mismatches; safety filtering blocks dangerous or unconfirmed calls; parallel execution reduces latency when the model requests multiple tools at once. Each layer is independently testable and composable \u2014 building them as pure functions lets you swap policies, add logging, or extend the safety rules without touching the executor."
